
Working Heroku Java/J2EE Salesforce App
=======================================

Basic integration between several frameworks, including:
Spring MVC 3.1.2.RELEASE
Hibernate ORM 4.2
Salesforce Java SDK 
Tomcat 7

For comments and requests: https://twitter.com/#!/tquila_nik


Env vars:
heroku config:add FORCE_PERSISTENCEUNIT_URL="force://[login|test].salesforce.com?user=<USERNAME>&password=<PASSWORD><SECURITYTOKEN>"
